        <h3>Source</h3>
                                    <div class="element-text">Photo © The Israel Museum, Jerusalem, Wapo Creek, Papuan Gulf, , Melanesia, Cane, wood, bark cloth, canvas, paint, fiber, Accession number: B85.0350, &lt;a class=&quot;external&quot; href=&quot;http://www.imj.org.il/imagine/collections/item.asp?itemNum=224467&quot;&gt;http://www.imj.org.il/imagine/collections/item.asp?itemNum=224467&lt;/a&gt; (accessed March 26, 2010). Annotated by Susan Douglass.</div>
                    </div><!-- end element -->
            <div id="dublin-core-publisher" class="element">
        <h3>Publisher</h3>
                    <div class="element-text-empty">[no text]</div>
            </div><!-- end element -->
